Q10.Write a Java Program to print the sum of the first and last digit of a 3-digit number.
import java.util.Scanner;
public class Main
{
public static void main(String args[])
{
    Scanner sc=new Scanner(System.in);
    int dig=sc.nextInt();
    int firstdig=dig/100;
    int lastdig=dig%10;
    System.out.println("Sum of first and last digit in given 3-digit number is:      "+(firstdig+lastdig));
}
}

Q11.Write a Java Program to print the middle digit of a 3-digit number.
