    public static void main(String args[])
    {
        int km=3;
        int meters=km*1000;
        System.out.println("Meters: "+meters);
}
}

Q6.A computer networks student wants to convert bytes into bits. Since 1 byte = 8 bits, the program multiplies accordingly.
